    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device in the pre-market design-screening context described in the claim and requirement bindings.",
